{"title":"In the Drops: Maap training kit, Restrap Frame Strap, and James Witts’ new book","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/maap-training-kit","date":1686303586000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/maap-training-kit\">In the Drops: Maap training kit, Restrap Frame Strap, and James Witts’ new book</a></p>\n\n<p>As the pros battled it out at the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/criterium-du-dauphine-preview\" target=\"_blank\">Critérium du Dauphiné</a> this week, Robyn Davidson rounded up the latest <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/2023-pro-cycling-shari-bossuyt\" target=\"_blank\">highlights and lowlights from the peloton</a> while Pete Muir amused ourselves with <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/islay-cycling\" target=\"_blank\">a trip to a Scottish island</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Emma Cole kicked off her Tunisia Diaries series with a complete rundown of her <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/bikepacking-bike-fit\" target=\"_blank\">bike-fit</a> and the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/bikepacking-kit-list\" target=\"_blank\">packing list</a> she’s assembled for an epic ride to North Africa, before turning her attention to <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/ribble-gravel-ti\" target=\"_blank\">the bike that she’ll be doing it on</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Will Strickson took a look at the mud-spattered <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/danni-shrosbree-unbound-factor-ostro-gravel\" target=\"_blank\">Factor Ostro Gravel</a> that Danni Shrosbree rode to fourth place at Unbound Gravel, reviewed the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/specialized-sworks-evade-3-helmet-review\" target=\"_blank\">Specialized S-Works Evade 3 helmet</a> and gave us a complete guide to the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/tour-de-suisse-preview\" target=\"_blank\">Tour de Suisse.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Meanwhile Roval (allegedly) saved us roughly a foot in a sprint with its new <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/roval-rapide-cockpit\" target=\"_blank\">Rapide one-piece bar and stem</a> and we rounded up the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-gravel-bike-upgrades\" target=\"_blank\">best gravel bike upgrades</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>On to this week’s kit!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Maap Training kit</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-jersey-1-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Front and rear of Maap jersey\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-jersey-1-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-jersey-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-jersey-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-jersey-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-jersey-1-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-jersey-1-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-jersey-1-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-jersey-1-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-jersey-1-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-jersey-1.jpg 1800w\" /><figcaption>Matthew Loveridge / Cyclist</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Do we give Maap too much attention? Arguably, but then there are few more zeitgeisty brands just now and it’s hard not to be seduced by its mellow tones. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-shorts-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Front and rear of Maap shorts\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-shorts-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-shorts-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-shorts-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-shorts-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-shorts-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-shorts-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-shorts-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-shorts-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-shorts-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-shorts.jpg 1800w\" /><figcaption>Matthew Loveridge / Cyclist</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Maap’s Training kit for the bike comes in a vast range of colours and ticks the usual boxes for premium road kit: nice feeling fabrics, a racy cut, and well executed details like the zipped key pocket on the jersey and logos that are tasteful rather than billboard-esque.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-crew-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Front and rear of Maap sweatshirt\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-crew-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-crew-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-crew-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-crew-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-crew-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-crew-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-crew-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-crew-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-crew-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/maap-training-crew.jpg 1800w\" /><figcaption>Matthew Loveridge / Cyclist</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Training Crew meanwhile is decidedly un-racy, with a very relaxed fit. It looks like a standard sweater from afar but it’s actually DWR-coated with a fleecy lining, so potentially a good option for loitering after events or even low-intensity commuting when there’s a chill in the air. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Buy now from Maap:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong><a href=\"https://maap.cc/uk/products/training-jersey-mushroom\" target=\"_blank\">Men’s Training Jersey (£130)</a> / <a href=\"https://maap.cc/uk/products/womens-training-jersey-bermuda\" target=\"_blank\">Women’s Training Jersey (£130)</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"https://maap.cc/uk/products/training-bib-3-0-black-black\" target=\"_blank\">Men’s Training Bib 3.0 (£195)</a> / <a href=\"https://maap.cc/uk/products/womens-training-bib-3-0-black-black\" target=\"_blank\">Women’s Training Bib 3.0 (£195)</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"https://maap.cc/uk/products/training-crew-deep-green\" target=\"_blank\">Training Crew (£120)</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"https://maap.cc/uk/products/training-sock-black-deep-green\" target=\"_blank\">Training Sock (£18)</a></strong></li><li><a href=\"https://fave.co/3P8n286\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>MAAP CLEARANCE SALE (Here)</strong> Up to 54% off</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2><em>Riding with the Rocketmen</em> by James Witts</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/riding-with-the-rocketmen-james-witts-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Riding with the Rocketmen book\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/riding-with-the-rocketmen-james-witts-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/riding-with-the-rocketmen-james-witts-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/riding-with-the-rocketmen-james-witts-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/riding-with-the-rocketmen-james-witts-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/riding-with-the-rocketmen-james-witts-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/riding-with-the-rocketmen-james-witts-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/riding-with-the-rocketmen-james-witts-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/riding-with-the-rocketmen-james-witts-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/riding-with-the-rocketmen-james-witts.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption>Matthew Loveridge / Cyclist</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Frequent <em>Cyclist</em> contributor, pro cycling expert and all-round nice chap <a href=\"https://www.waterstones.com/book/riding-with-the-rocketmen/james-witts/9781399403504\" target=\"_blank\">James Witts</a> has a new book out. In <em>Riding with the Rocketmen</em>, a rather self-deprecating James embarks on an attempt to ride the 2022 <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/etape-du-tour-training\" target=\"_blank\">L’Étape du Tour sportive</a>, coming from a place of being not-all-that-fit. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>To get up to speed James decides to equip himself with the training techniques, gear and nutrition of a WorldTour pro, taking advantage of the unique access to riders and teams being a cycling journalist affords him. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>We’re looking forward to this one.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Buy now from <a href=\"https://www.waterstones.com/book/riding-with-the-rocketmen/james-witts/9781399403504\" target=\"_blank\">Waterstones (£14.99)</a></strong></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Restrap Frame Strap</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Frame strap\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption>Matthew Loveridge / Cyclist</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s a truth universally acknowledged that gravel riders love hanging things off their bikes. The new Restrap Frame Strap is a stout piece of kit measuring roughly 5cm wide by 47cm long, and it looks ideal for attaching extra tubes and the like directly to your frame. It weighs just under 40g on my scales.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-2-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Strap unfolded\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-2-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-2-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-2-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-2-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-2-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-2-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/restrap-frame-strap-2.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption>Matthew Loveridge / Cyclist</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Frame Strap is a little more sophisticated than a basic luggage strap, as an inner strap secures the cargo to the main strap, which in turn wraps around the frame. Can I say ‘strap’ any more times?</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Buy now from <a href=\"https://restrap.com/products/frame-strap\" target=\"_blank\">Restrap (£19.99)</a></strong></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>What we’re into this week: <em>Silo</em></h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"546\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/silo-apple-tv-970x546.jpg\" alt=\"Silo poster\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/silo-apple-tv-970x546.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/silo-apple-tv-300x169.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/silo-apple-tv-768x432.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/silo-apple-tv-750x422.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/silo-apple-tv-1140x641.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/06/silo-apple-tv.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption>Apple TV+</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>There are a lot of big concept TV shows around now and, in truth, most of them suck. Apple TV+’s <em>Silo</em>, however, has me thoroughly hooked. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Starring Rebecca Ferguson (Swedish actor, not Liverpudlian singer), the world of <em>Silo</em> is entirely underground, one where humanity lives a bunkered (siloed?) existence. Its history has been erased and the outside world is, as far as we know, uninhabitable. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s a sweaty, claustrophobic drama with a great cast and some well-sustained intrigue: what’s really outside? What happened 140 years ago? Where does all the poo go? I still don’t know, but I’m desperate to find out.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://tv.apple.com/us/show/silo/umc.cmc.3yksgc857px0k0rqe5zd4jice\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Watch Silo on Apple TV+</strong></a></li></ul>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h3><span>Related Posts</span></h3>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                  